      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/683ba087a461e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/683ba0bf4119c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/683ba0cc2c59f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/683ba0f6309b1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/683ba0fcb2c41.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Change&lt;/em&gt;: Added in a custom birthday matching her sign&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Change&lt;/em&gt;: Added name change within the mod&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Change&lt;/em&gt;: Made expressions more faithful to her original appearance&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Change&lt;/em&gt;: You can pick if she's peppy or sisterly personality&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Change&lt;/em&gt;: Fixed an issue that made it so her ears weren't colored properly from behind.&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Change&lt;/em&gt;: Her picture is now custom, instead of using her ereader pic.&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;I brought back another removed villager!&lt;br&gt;Penny replaces Greta&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Update 4 years later.. i know im lazy..&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;It now includes her minigame icon, her photo, her catchphrase, name change and custom birthday matching her sign in the e-reader card.&lt;br&gt;If you want her house to look how it did on the original game you can edit it using the acnl save editor.&lt;br&gt;You can pick between her having a peppy personality and a sisterly personality in the new update&lt;br&gt;I've also made her expressions more faithful to how they were in the original game and fixed an issue that made it so the behind of her ears weren't colored properly.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Put the romfs folder on: \luma\titles\gameid&lt;game title="" class="SelectedElement"&gt;\romfs&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Note for those who already have custom villagers in their town:&lt;br&gt;Since this mod includes her pic and also the name change, if you have any other custom villagers&lt;br&gt;that also have their name edited or photo item name altered,&amp;nbsp; they'll no longer have those changes&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Since the file included in this mod only edits Pennys name / Penny's photo item name.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If you wouldnt like this to happen, just edit her name in the file you already have in the scripts folder manually using a hex editor by following this tutorial:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;https://juette.tumblr.com/post/716504689334681600/a-comprehensive-guide-to-custom-villagers&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Last update i have planned for this is to hex edit her house interior so you dont need to mess with the save editor to do it.&lt;/game&gt;</description>
